    <entry>
      <title>建设问题及解决</title>
      <link href="/Blog_backup/2026/06/29/%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3/"/>
      <url>/Blog_backup/2026/06/29/%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="建设过程中遇到的问题及解决"><a href="#建设过程中遇到的问题及解决" class="headerlink" title="建设过程中遇到的问题及解决"></a>建设过程中遇到的问题及解决</h1><hr><h2 id="一、Node-js-环境问题"><a href="#一、Node-js-环境问题" class="headerlink" title="一、Node.js 环境问题"></a>一、Node.js 环境问题</h2><blockquote><p><strong>问题描述</strong>：终端显示没有 node 版本被激活，导致 hexo 命令无法执行。</p></blockquote><h3 id="解决方法"><a href="#解决方法" class="headerlink" title="解决方法"></a>解决方法</h3><p><strong>1. 激活 nvm</strong></p><p>在 zsh 里运行：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> ~/.nvm/nvm.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>2. 查看已安装的 Node 版本</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nvm list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>3. 选择一个 Node 版本</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nvm use 20</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>4. 确认版本</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="二、文章封面默认设置未生效"><a href="#二、文章封面默认设置未生效" class="headerlink" title="二、文章封面默认设置未生效"></a>二、文章封面默认设置未生效</h2><blockquote><p><strong>问题描述</strong>：在 <code>_config.butterfly.yml</code> 中设置的 <code>default_top_img</code> 路径没有生效。</p></blockquote><h3 id="解决方法-1"><a href="#解决方法-1" class="headerlink" title="解决方法"></a>解决方法</h3><p><strong>错误写法</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">default_top_img:</span> <span class="string">/source/images/top.jpg</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>正确写法</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">default_top_img:</span> <span class="string">/images/top.jpg</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>原因</strong>：<code>/images/1.jpg</code> 会指向 <code>source/images/1.jpg</code>，这是 Hexo 的约定，生成时会自动复制到 <code>public/images/1.jpg</code>。</p><blockquote><p><strong>注意</strong>：YAML 语法要求冒号后必须有空格。</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="三、Hexo-手动部署问题"><a href="#三、Hexo-手动部署问题" class="headerlink" title="三、Hexo 手动部署问题"></a>三、Hexo 手动部署问题</h2><blockquote><p><strong>问题描述</strong>：修改了文章日期后，执行 <code>hexo deploy</code> 部署，但网站内容没有更新，文章页面出现 404 错误。</p></blockquote><h3 id="问题分析"><a href="#问题分析" class="headerlink" title="问题分析"></a>问题分析</h3><ol><li><p><strong>目录混淆</strong>：有两个相关目录</p><ul><li><code>~/BlogProject/Blog_backup</code> — Hexo 源码仓库（对应 <code>Blog_backup.git</code>）</li><li><code>~/BlogProject/Blog_pages</code> — GitHub Pages 仓库（对应 <code>XianZe1226.github.io.git</code>）</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>缓存问题</strong>：之前没有清除 Hexo 缓存就直接部署，导致旧内容没有被更新。</p></li></ol><h3 id="解决方法-2"><a href="#解决方法-2" class="headerlink" title="解决方法"></a>解决方法</h3><p><strong>正确的 Hexo 部署三连</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo generate &amp;&amp; hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><code>hexo clean</code> — 清除缓存和 <code>public/</code> 目录</li><li><code>hexo generate</code> — 重新生成静态文件</li><li><code>hexo deploy</code> — 部署到 GitHub Pages</li></ul><blockquote><p><strong>注意</strong>：修改内容后一定要执行完整的三连命令，否则可能出现缓存不更新或 404 错误。</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="四、GitHub-Actions-自动部署问题"><a href="#四、GitHub-Actions-自动部署问题" class="headerlink" title="四、GitHub Actions 自动部署问题"></a>四、GitHub Actions 自动部署问题</h2><blockquote><p><strong>问题描述</strong>：配置了 GitHub Actions 自动部署到 GitHub Pages，但部署后网站布局严重错乱，CSS 样式和 JS 脚本全部丢失。</p></blockquote><h3 id="问题分析-1"><a href="#问题分析-1" class="headerlink" title="问题分析"></a>问题分析</h3><ol><li><p><strong><code>.gitignore</code> 误排除</strong>：在 <code>.gitignore</code> 中添加了 <code>css/</code>、<code>js/</code> 等规则来排除源码仓库中的生成文件，但这些规则同时影响了 GitHub Actions 的部署流程，导致 <code>public/</code> 目录中的 CSS&#x2F;JS 文件没有被推送到 <code>gh-pages</code> 分支。</p></li><li><p><strong>主题源文件未提交</strong>：Butterfly 主题的 <code>themes/butterfly/source/</code> 目录（包含 <code>.styl</code> 样式源文件和 <code>.js</code> 脚本文件）没有被 git 跟踪。GitHub Actions 在远端构建时找不到这些文件，导致 Stylus 无法编译成 CSS，JS 文件也无法被复制。</p></li><li><p><strong>路径问题</strong>：<code>_config.butterfly.yml</code> 中 <code>inject.head</code> 里的 <code>custom.css</code> 路径是硬编码的 <code>/css/custom.css</code>，部署到子路径（<code>/Blog_backup/</code>）后需要改为 <code>/Blog_backup/css/custom.css</code>。</p></li></ol><h3 id="解决方法-3"><a href="#解决方法-3" class="headerlink" title="解决方法"></a>解决方法</h3><p><strong>1. 精简 <code>.gitignore</code></strong>，只保留必要的排除项：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.DS_Store</span><br><span class="line">Thumbs.db</span><br><span class="line">db.json</span><br><span class="line">*.log</span><br><span class="line">node_modules/</span><br><span class="line">public/</span><br><span class="line">.deploy*/</span><br><span class="line">_multiconfig.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>不要添加 <code>css/</code>、<code>js/</code>、<code>images/</code> 等规则，否则会影响 GitHub Actions 部署。</p></blockquote><p><strong>2. 确保主题源文件已提交</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git add themes/butterfly/source/</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m <span class="string">&quot;添加主题源文件&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>3. 安装主题依赖</strong>（<code>package.json</code> 中需包含）：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-stylus hexo-renderer-pug --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>4. 配置 GitHub Actions workflow</strong>（<code>.github/workflows/deploy.yml</code>）：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Deploy</span> <span class="string">Hexo</span> <span class="string">to</span> <span class="string">GitHub</span> <span class="string">Pages</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">on:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">push:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">branches:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">permissions:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">contents:</span> <span class="string">write</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">jobs:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">build-and-deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">runs-on:</span> <span class="string">ubuntu-latest</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">steps:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Checkout</span> <span class="string">source</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">uses:</span> <span class="string">actions/checkout@v4</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Setup</span> <span class="string">Node.js</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">uses:</span> <span class="string">actions/setup-node@v4</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">with:</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">node-version:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;20&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Install</span> <span class="string">dependencies</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">run:</span> <span class="string">npm</span> <span class="string">install</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Clean</span> <span class="string">and</span> <span class="string">Generate</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">run:</span> <span class="string">npx</span> <span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">clean</span> <span class="string">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class="string">npx</span> <span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">generate</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Deploy</span> <span class="string">to</span> <span class="string">gh-pages</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">uses:</span> <span class="string">JamesIves/github-pages-deploy-action@v4</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">with:</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">gh-pages</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">folder:</span> <span class="string">public</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">clean:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>5. 仓库设置</strong>：在 GitHub 仓库的 Settings → Pages → Source 中选择 <code>gh-pages</code> 分支。</p><h3 id="部署流程总结"><a href="#部署流程总结" class="headerlink" title="部署流程总结"></a>部署流程总结</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">本地修改文章</span><br><span class="line">    ↓</span><br><span class="line">git add / git commit / git push</span><br><span class="line">    ↓</span><br><span class="line">GitHub Actions 自动触发</span><br><span class="line">    ↓</span><br><span class="line">npm install（安装依赖）</span><br><span class="line">    ↓</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo generate（生成静态文件）</span><br><span class="line">    ↓</span><br><span class="line">JamesIves action 部署到 gh-pages 分支</span><br><span class="line">    ↓</span><br><span class="line">GitHub Pages 自动更新网站</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p><strong>注意</strong>：<code>.gitignore</code> 中的规则会影响 GitHub Actions 的部署，不要添加排除生成文件的规则。主题的 <code>source/</code> 目录必须提交到 git，否则远端构建时 CSS&#x2F;JS 无法生成。</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
